CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Oklo is developing next-generation fission reactors to produce abundant, affordable, clean energy at a global scale - starting with the Aurora, which can produce 15 MW of electrical power, scalable to 50 MWe, and operate for 10 years or longer before refueling. Oklo's fast reactors incorporate inherent safety features and can be fueled by recycled waste.
